data.description: Discover the epitome of luxury Country living in this remarkable 4-bedroom home, nestled on 7 picturesque acres with a massive 56x60 Shop and RV Parking. With 2 full baths and one half bath, this property seamlessly combines elegance and practicality. Upon entering, the open floorplan welcomes you with charming shiplap accents, and a dedicated office space with French doors. The kitchen, with its rich granite countertops and abundant cabinetry, is a culinary paradise. Tile floors grace the entire home, offering style and durability. Safety and efficiency are top priorities, with an above-ground storm shelter, Class 4 roof, and spray foam insulation. The standout feature of this property is the massive 56x60 shop, complemented by RV parking, providing ample space for hobbies or storage.
